1991;;Together Alone;;American;;P.J. Castellaneta;;Terry Curry, Todd Stites;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Together_Alone_(film);;Bryan meets a man called Bill in a bar. They go back to Bryan's home and have unprotected sex. Later, they wake up and talk. Bryan discovers that Bill's real name is Brian, and that he is bisexual. They spend hours talking, covering topics including AIDS, sexuality, feminism, role-play and Emily Dickinson.[1]